Class CharBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.tamchow.fractal.helpers.strings.CharBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.CharSequence, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<CharBuffer>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResizableCharBuffer

    public class CharBuffer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.CharSequence, java.lang.Comparable<CharBuffer>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Little-nonsense Character Buffer which is faster than StringBuilder. Does not cache String representation for performance reasons.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
